OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mainly dry
OL,6,Fstart to the evening once rain clears
OL,7,FShetland. Later in the night outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain will spread into Orkney then
OL,9,FShetland. Fresh southerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy morning with
OL,12,Fscattered showers. Turning brighter
OL,13,Fthrough the afternoon with some
OL,14,Fsunnier spells developing and showers
OL,15,Fbecoming fewer. Fresh to strong winds.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloud
OL,18,Fand rain or showers on Sunday. Turning
OL,19,Fdrier with some sunnier spells on
OL,20,FMonday and Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
